* Changelog [23rd December 2021]
* Happy Holidays everyone!
* Upstreamed latest QuickSilveR source
* USB-OTG Fixed
* Upstreamed Wireguard to 202111208
* Now compiled with LLVM-Polly optimization
* Added support for NTFS_RW
* Added support for exFAT-arter97
* Added experimental support for DriveDroid
* Removed support for Nintendo Joycons
* Fixes for better battery backup
* Addressed a few logspam issues.
* Other misc optimizations
